---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-surface-lighter bg-surface-light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xl">🦆</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
          藍鴨 LaunchDock — 弄髒雙手，但不孤單
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/589411/launchdock"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-text-muted hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="/#discussion"
          class="text-text-muted hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          討論區
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-text-muted text-xs mt-4">
      &copy; {year} 藍鴨 LaunchDock. Built with Astro.
    </p>
    <p class="text-center text-text-muted text-xs mt-2 opacity-70">
      本站為 OpenClaw 開源專案教學社群，與其他同名軟體無關。
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
